                        <span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: #FFFFFF; ">Cargo Fijo Promocional</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <span id="fixedChargePromotional" class="pull-right" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: #FFFFFF;">S/ 0.00</span>
